    "messageBody": "<div id=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686\">\n<html><head>\n \n\n\n</head> \n\n \n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\">I agree with what Sachin said, \nwith one minor change. There is another member function in Assert called fail() \nwhich you can use:</span></font></div>\n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\"></span></font>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\">public void testXXX( ) throws \nException</span></font></div>\n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\">{</span></font></div>\n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\">&nbsp; try</span></font></div>\n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\">&nbsp; {</span></font></div>\n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \ndoMyStuffThatMightThrow( );</span></font></div>\n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; fail( \n&quot;Didn&#39;t get my expected exception&quot; );</span></font></div>\n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\">&nbsp; }</span></font></div>\n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\">&nbsp; catch( \nMyExpectedException e )</span></font></div>\n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\">&nbsp; {</span></font></div>\n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\">&nbsp; }</span></font></div>\n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\">}</span></font></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\">Same thing as the previous \nposter, just replace his assert( false ) with fail().</span></font></div>\n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\"></span></font>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><font size=\"2\"><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686269200513-19122000\">bab</span></font></div>\n<p><font size=\"2\">----<br>Brian Button&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \nbbutton@...<br>Senior Consultant&nbsp; Object Mentor, Inc.</font> \n</p>\n<blockquote><span title=\"qreply\"> <blockquote\n style=\"BORDER-LEFT:#000000 2px solid;MARGIN-LEFT:5px;PADDING-LEFT:5px;\">\n  <div align=\"left\" class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686OutlookMessageHeader\" dir=\"ltr\"><font face=\"Tahoma\"\n size=\"2\">-----Original Message-----<br><b>From:</b> sachin gupta \n  [mailto:sachin@...]<br><b>Sent:</b> Tuesday, December 19, 2000 12:29 \n  AM<br><b>To:</b> junit@egroups.com<br><b>Subject:</b> RE: [junit] Exception \n  Handling Question<br><br></font></div>\n  <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686992582106-19122000\"><font size=\"2\">In case Exception is \n  mentioned in the throws clause of method you may try something like this \n  </font></span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686992582106-19122000\"><font size=\"2\"></font></span>&nbsp;</div>\n  <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686992582106-19122000\"><font size=\"2\">try </font></span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686992582106-19122000\"><font size=\"2\">{</font></span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686992582106-19122000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <font size=\"2\">method \n  with input that causes the expected Exception to be \nthrown.</font></span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686992582106-19122000\"><font size=\"2\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \n  assert(false);</font></span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686992582106-19122000\"><font size=\"2\">}</font></span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686992582106-19122000\"><font size=\"2\">catch (ExpectedException \n  e)</font></span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686992582106-19122000\"><font size=\"2\">{</font></span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686992582106-19122000\"><font\n size=\"2\">assert(true);</font></span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"ygrps-yiv-1584061686992582106-19122000\"><font\n size=\"2\">}</font></span></div></blockquote></span></blockquote></html> \n</div>", 
